<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>결제 완료</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background: #f9f9f9;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
        color: #333;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 500px;
        margin: 50px auto;
        background: white;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h1 {
        color: #4caf50;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      a.button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        background-color: #d32f2f;
        color: white;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      a.button:hover {
        background-color: #b71c1c;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>결제 완료</h1>
      <p>장바구니 비우면서 결제해주셔서 감사합니다!</p>
      <a href="/resource" class="button">쇼핑 계속하기</a>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
